Title: See You Up There
Writer: Albert Dupontel (adaptation), Pierre Lemaitre (participation), Pierre Lemaitre (book)
Actors: Nahuel Pérez Biscayart, Albert Dupontel, Laurent Lafitte, Niels Arestrup
Plot: November 1919. Two soldiers - a disfigured but brilliant artist and an ex-accountant - start a memorial con. But in the France of the Roaring Twenties, their adventures soon turn dangerous.
